plot: It's two firsts for Mark: a first date and a first trip to another planet. At the same time, Nolan and Debbie revisit their own first vacation together.

Invincible secretly escorts humanity's first mission to Mars when his father refuses. Meanwhile, Mark deal with his first date with Amber, and finds himself in an awkward position when he has to lie to her about gong to Mars. Damien grows closer to learning Nolan's secret, and Cecil takes steps to stop the demon before he reveals to Nolan that he's under investigation.—Gislef
